            "bicycleTabs_contentHeader": "Waterproof Rear Basket Bag",
            "bicycleTabs_contentDesc": "The electric cargo trike provides a storage basket with a waterproof bag, which perfectly fit with the rear basket. A large-capacity with 48L, easy loading with heavy objects."
          }
        }
