          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The differential exists to adjust the speed difference between the left and right wheels so that when the MF-30 is driving on uneven roads or turning, the left and right wheels can roll at different speeds. To achieve the purpose of ensuring the overall balance and safety of the electric tricycle when passing through special terrain or turning.</p>",
            "text_style": "subtitle"
          }
